name: Artia, the lifetaker
description: Artia the youngest daughter of the cosmic mother. while she is the youngest do not mistake her for her power is truly beyond compare. she earned the name lifetaker for she used to be the lover of death himself but she do not want a lover she merely use death for the teachings that death himself could give to her. Her brother on the other hand, the world ender is the only person that ever truly loved her.
